  "suggested_payload_hint": "regression test: spawn EnvBuilder::up under a #[tokio::test], drop the RunningEnv inside `tokio::task::spawn_blocking(|| panic!())`, observe via `docker compose ls --format json --filter project=<name>` that the project disappears within DOWN_TIMEOUT. Today the test will time out on macOS because the detached worker dies with the parent before reaching kill()."
}

